    feat(zip): add fflate-based ZIP package library

    vendor/fflate.umd.js — pure-JS fflate UMD bundle (~32 KB, no deps).
    Chosen because the webapp must run strict-offline (no CDN); fflate
    is small enough to vendor inline alongside the existing PDF.js + jsPDF
    + Noto fonts.

    lib/zip_core.js — thin wrapper exposing ZipCore.{readZip, writeZip,
    makePackageZip} for the Open/Save Package ZIP buttons in the webapp.
    A mirrored copy lives in indesign-toolkit/translation_mvp_uxp/lib/
    zip_core.js so the InDesign UXP side and the webapp share the same
    package read/write contract.

